1
00:00:01,958 --> 00:00:03,750
Want a convenient and secure way

2
00:00:03,750 --> 00:00:06,666
to access your Government of Canada services and benefits?

3
00:00:07,250 --> 00:00:09,833
Register for My Service Canada Account today!

4
00:00:10,250 --> 00:00:15,458
<font color="blue">This</font> <b>account</b> gives <i>you</i> secure <u>access</u> to services and benefits
related to the <font color="red"><b><i><u>Canada</u></i></b></font> Pension Plan,

5
00:00:15,750 --> 00:00:18,833
Old Age Security and Employment Insurance.

6
00:00:19,333 --> 00:00:23,791
You can also sign up for direct deposit
to have your payments sent directly to your bank account.

7
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:27,500
To register, you’ll need to provide some personal information,

8
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,583
including your date of birth and Social Insurance Number.

9
00:00:30,958 --> 00:00:34,041
For safety and security, you will need to validate your identity

10
00:00:34,041 --> 00:00:38,541
with a personal access code
or by using the <i>Interac</i>® verification service.

11
00:00:38,541 --> 00:00:40,166
Don’t have a personal access code?

12
00:00:40,166 --> 00:00:44,750
Don’t worry, you can request one online,
by phone or at a Service Canada Centre.

13
00:00:45,250 --> 00:00:47,291
The <i>Interac</i>® verification service

14
00:00:47,291 --> 00:00:50,166
will allow you to register for My Service Canada Account

15
00:00:50,166 --> 00:00:54,333
safely and instantly by using your online
banking information.

16
00:00:55,583 --> 00:01:00,500
To put your mind at ease, we have added multi-factor
authentication to help protect your account!

17
00:01:01,125 --> 00:01:03,958
Once registered, there are three ways to sign in.

18
00:01:03,958 --> 00:01:08,958
You can sign in with your GCKey, with a sign-in partner,
such as your bank,

19
00:01:09,333 --> 00:01:14,208
or with your provincial digital ID
if you live in British Columbia or Alberta.

20
00:01:14,208 --> 00:01:17,541
Each one of the three sign-in options is safe and secure!

21
00:01:17,541 --> 00:01:21,333
And you can do it all from your computer, phone or tablet.

22
00:01:21,750 --> 00:01:25,875
Register now to see all the advantages
My Service Canada Account has to offer!

23
00:01:26,416 --> 00:01:31,666
Visit canada.ca/MyServiceCanadaAccount to register.
